        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Help Ensure Lives are Protected Act of 2019 or the HELP Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill establishes enhanced criminal penalties&#8212;life imprisonment or death&#8212;for certain drug offenses involving fentanyl that result in death or serious bodily injury. </p>]]></text>
